g.text: Place FlashROM_100 into the DIP-28 socket.
Install jumpers on the ~CS~ and PROGRAM pins.
This for the 29F010 FlashROM_100, not the 28C256 FlexROM_100.
2 address lines are not connected (32k vs 128k), so there will always be size mismatch and write verification errors when programming.
